\s  MWAMI WANJE NDAKWIHAYE NDAKWIHEREJE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Mwami wanje ndakwihaye ndakwihereje, nizeye y’uk’utazigera umpemuki-ra, warapfuye urazuka non’uri \bd*\bd Muzima,  .\bd*\bd /.N’undinde mu ngendo zose ziy’isi Mwami./.\bd*
